---
import { Image } from 'astro:assets';
import RedLogo from '../assets/LOGOTYPE-RE-HORIZONTAL-ROUGE.svg';
import WhiteLogo from '../assets/LOGOTYPE-RE-HORIZONTAL-BLANC.svg';
import RightArrow from '../assets/right-arrow.svg';
---

<header class="">
  <nav>
    <div class="wrapper">
      <div class="nav-column first-nav-column flex items-center">
        <div class="logo">
          <a href="/">
            <Image id="red-logo" src={RedLogo} alt="Règles élémentaires" />
            <Image id="white-logo" src={WhiteLogo} alt="Règles élémentaires" />
          </a>
        </div>
        <input type="checkbox" name="menu" id="menu-btn">
        <label for="menu-btn" class="ms-4">
          <svg id="menu-svg" role="img" aria-label="Menu" width="39" height="39" viewBox="0 0 39 39" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
            <rect x="0.5" y="0.5" width="37.8281" height="37.8281" rx="4.5"/>
            <line x1="8.26572" y1="11.7031" x2="30.5626" y2="11.7031" stroke-linecap="round"/>
            <line x1="8.26553" y1="19.1914" x2="30.5624" y2="19.1914" stroke-linecap="round"/>
            <line x1="8.26553" y1="27.5117" x2="30.5624" y2="27.5117" stroke-linecap="round"/>
          </svg>
        </label>
      </div>
      <div class="nav-column second-nav-column"></div>
      <div class="nav-column third-nav-column flex justify-end">
        <div class="nav-right-buttons">
          <a class="small-maroon-shadow font-lorimer bg-rebeige-300 text-remaroon p-2.5 me-4" href="/">Ressources</a>
          <a class="small-maroon-shadow font-lorimer bg-rered text-rebeige-300 p-2.5" href="/">Faire un don</a>
        </div>        
      </div>
    </div>
    <div id="mega-box">
        <div class="content">
          <div class="nav-column bg-rered ps-15 py-6">
            <ul class="mega-links text-rebeige-300">
              <li><a href="#">Qui sommes-nous ?</a></li>
              <li><a id="nos-actions-link" href="#">Nos actions</a></li>
              <li><a href="#">Notre impact</a></li>
              <li><a id="sengager-link" href="#">S'engager</a></li>
              <li><a href="#">S'informer</a></li>
              <li><a href="#">Notre plaidoyer</a></li>
            </ul>
          </div>
          <div class="nav-column bg-remaroon py-6">
            <div id="mega-actu" class="text-rebeige-300 px-6 flex flex-col">
              <div>
                <span class="square-button inline-block bg-rered text-rebeige-300 text-2xl">Actualité à la une</span>
              </div>              
              <span class="font-lorimer-condensed text-4xl mt-6">Actu à venir</span>
              <p class="font-extrabold text-sm mt-2">20 mars 2026</p>
              <p class="mt-2">Dorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit. Etiam eu turpis molestie, dictum est a, mattis tellus. Sed dignissim, metus nec fringilla accumsan, r adipiscing elit. Etiam eu turpis molestie, dictu</p>
              <div class="mt-2">
                <a href="#" class="inline-block">
                  <div class="flex items-center">
                      <div class="bg-rebeige-300 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center h-10 w-10 border-4 border-remaroon -me-4 z-200">
                          <Image class="w-2/3" src={RightArrow} alt="" />
                      </div>    
                      <div class="bg-rebeige-300 text-remaroon font-bold text-sm ps-6 py-0.5 pe-2">Voir toutes les actus</div>
                  </div>
                </a>
              </div>              
            </div>
            <ul id="mega-nos-actions-submenu" class="text-rebeige-300">
              <li><a href="#">Lutter contre la précarité menstruelle</a></li>
              <li><a href="#">Déployer l'éducation menstruelle</a></li>
              <li><a href="#">Informer</a></li>
              <li><a href="#">Former</a></li>
              <li><a href="#">Mobiliser</a></li>
              <li><a href="#">Changer les règles</a></li>
              <li><a href="#">Actions à l’échelle européenne</a></li>
            </ul>
            <ul id="mega-sengager-submenu" class="text-rebeige-300">
              <li><a href="#">Faire un don</a></li>
              <li><a href="#">Organiser une collecte</a></li>
              <li><a href="#">Devenir bénévole</a></li>
              <li><a href="#">Devenir partenaire</a></li>
              <li><a href="#">Devenir une entreprise engagée</a></li>
              <li><a href="#">Devenir une collectivité engagée</a></li>
              <li><a href="#">Devenir un établissement engagé</a></li>
            </ul>
          </div>
          <div class="nav-column bg-rebeige-100 flex-wrap">
            <div class="w-full flex py-8 pe-15">
              <div class="w-5/12">
                
              </div>
              <div class="w-7/12">
                <p>Notre solution pour généraliser l’éducation menstruelle</p>
                <a class="small-maroon-shadow inline-block font-lorimer bg-rebeige-300 text-remaroon p-2.5 me-4 mt-2" href="/">En savoir plus</a>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="w-full flex bg-rebeige-300 py-8 pe-15">
              <div class="w-5/12">
                
              </div>
              <div class="w-7/12">
                <p>Notre solution pour mobiliser et lutter contre la précarité menstruelle</p>
                <a class="small-maroon-shadow inline-block font-lorimer bg-rebeige-300 text-remaroon p-2.5 me-4 mt-2" href="/">En savoir plus</a>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="w-full flex flex-col bg-regreen py-6 ps-6 pe-15">
              <span class="font-lorimer-condensed text-remaroon text-4xl">Nos ressources</span>
              <div class="mt-2">
                <a href="#" class="inline-block">
                  <div class="flex items-center">
                      <div class="bg-rebeige-300 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center h-10 w-10 border-4 border-regreen -me-4 z-200">
                          <Image class="w-2/3" src={RightArrow} alt="" />
                      </div>    
                      <div class="bg-rebeige-300 text-remaroon font-bold text-sm ps-6 py-0.5 pe-2">Voir toutes les ressources</div>
                  </div>
                </a>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
  </nav>
</header>